************************************************************************
                           How to install
************************************************************************

For prerequisites see README file.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Decompress the accULL-dev.tar.gz file
	$ cd ~
	$ tar xvzf accULL-dev.tar.gz

2. Set the right path to environment variables in file env-parameters.sh.
	$ cd accULL-dev
	$ vim env-parameters.sh
	
3. Configure and compile accULL.
	$./build-accull.sh

4. Verify the settings of the yacf/config_local.py 
   $ $EDITOR yacf/config_local.py

4. Check your installation. 
	$ source env-parameters.sh
	$ cd example  # PI problem in OpenACC
	$ make
	$ cd accull_*/pi.acc.c/Frangollo  
	$./main.exe

